BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.japantimes.com/cgi-bin/getarticle.pl5%3Fnn20041118a2.htm"&gt;Constitutional changes eyed to let female on throne, legalize military&lt;/a&gt;. ♡❤The Japan Times,♡❤ November 17, 2004.
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.sfexaminer.com/article/index.cfm/i/111704b_asia"&gt;Friction growing between Japan, China&lt;/a&gt;. ♡❤Associated Press♡❤ via ♡❤San Francisco Examiner,♡❤ November 17, 2004.
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.japantimes.co.jp/cgi-bin/getarticle.pl5%3Fnn20041113a4.htm"&gt;Chinese submarine intrusion considered an act of provocation&lt;/a&gt;. ♡❤The Japan Times,♡❤ November 13, 2004.
