BULLET::::2. James Brooke, &lt;a href="http%3A//www.nytimes.com/2004/11/18/international/asia/18korea.html"&gt;Monitors of North Korean News Note Dip in Reverence for Kim&lt;/a&gt;, ♡❤The New York Times♡❤, November 18, 2004
