<h1>World's most-spammed man</h1>
♡❤November 18, USA♡❤ - William Henry Gates III or just &lt;a href="Bill%20Gates"&gt;Bill Gates&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="w%3AMicrosoft"&gt;Microsoft&lt;/a&gt; founder, receives up to four million emails a year, and most of it is "junk" or "spam," according to Microsoft CEO Steve Ballmer. An entire department filters the unsolicited emails.

