<h1>Longhorn for 2006, according to Gates</h1>
&lt;/center&gt; 
<h2>Sources</h2>
<ul>
BULLET::::- Ina Fried and Margaret Kane. "&lt;a href="http%3A//software.silicon.com/os/0%2C39024651%2C39123578%2C00.htm"&gt;Microsoft reveals latest on Longhorn release&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3Asilicon.com"&gt;silicon.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, August 31, 2004
