BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//spj.org/pressNotes.asp%3Fref%3D8642"&gt;SPJ PressNotes for Thursday, November 18, 2004&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ASociety%20of%20Professional%20Journalists"&gt;Society of Professional Journalists&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, November 18, 2004
