BULLET::::2. Aung Hla Tun, &lt;a href="http%3A//www.reuters.com/newsArticle.jhtml%3Ftype%3DworldNews%26amp%3BstoryID%3D6870249"&gt;Myanmar Frees Prominent Political Prisoners&lt;/a&gt;, ♡❤Reuters♡❤, November 20, 2004.
BULLET::::3. &lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/4027667.stm"&gt;UN hails Burma inmates' release&lt;/a&gt;, ♡❤BBC♡❤, November 20, 2004.

