BULLET::::- Pentagon Says It Will Open Tanker Deal To Competition «u&gt;&lt;a href="http%3A//www.komotv.com/boeing/story.asp%3FID%3D34087"&gt;broken link&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u» — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AKOMO%201000%20News"&gt;KOMO 1000 News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, November 22, 2004
