<doc id="1181" url="https://en.wikinews.org/wiki?curid=1181" title="Ukraine election results delayed by court">
<h1>Ukraine election results delayed by court</h1>
Steven Lee Myers. "&lt;a href="http%3A//nytimes.com/2004/11/29/international/europe/29cnd-ukra.html%3Fhp%26amp%3Bex%3D1101790800%26amp%3Ben%3D93f5ca7f542c1962%26amp%3Bei%3D5094%26amp%3Bpartner%3Dwikipedia"&gt;A Silent Act of Rebellion Raises a Din in Ukraine&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20New%20York%20Times"&gt;The New York Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, November 29, 2004 


