BULLET::::- ♡❤BBC♡❤, November 28, 2004: &lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/asia-pacific/4049069.stm"&gt;China mine blast traps 170 workers&lt;/a&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/1/low/world/asia-pacific/3206645.stm"&gt;China industry deaths in 2003&lt;/a&gt;

