BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//makelovenotspam.com/intl/index.html"&gt;Make LOVE not SPAM&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ALycos"&gt;Lycos&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, Accessed 29 November 2004
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/technology/4051553.stm"&gt;Screensaver tackles spam websites&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC%20Online"&gt;BBC Online&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, 29 November 2004
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.siliconvalleynorth.com/home/newsGeyWBmzllk20041129.html"&gt;Take Part in your Very Own DDoS Attack&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ASilicon%20Valley%20North"&gt;Silicon Valley North&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, November 29, 2004
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//p2pnet.net/story/3150"&gt;Make Love, not Spam!&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3Ap2pnet.net%20News"&gt;p2pnet.net News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, November 29, 2004
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.heise.de/english/newsticker/news/53697"&gt;Lycos users are to attack spammers&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AHeise%20Online"&gt;Heise Online&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, November 26, 2004

</ul>
