BULLET::::- Deb Riechmann. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.kansascity.com/mld/kansascity/news/world/10306675.htm%3F1c"&gt;Bush Grateful for 'Five-Finger' Welcome&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, November 30, 2004
BULLET::::- IMC Ottawa. "&lt;a href="http%3A//ottawa.indymedia.ca/en/2004/11/84.shtml"&gt;15,000 demonstrate&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AIndependent%20Media%20Center"&gt;Independent Media Center&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, November 30, 2004
