BULLET::::- kaisernetwork.org. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.kaisernetwork.org/daily_reports/rep_index.cfm%3FDR_ID%3D22603"&gt;Daily Reproductive Health Report&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3Akaisernetwork.org"&gt;kaisernetwork.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, 10 March, 2004
BULLET::::- Brian Wingfield. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.nytimes.com/2004/12/03/politics/03abstinence.html"&gt;Study Faults Abstinence Courses&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ANew%20York%20Times"&gt;New York Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, December 2, 2004
BULLET::::- Bill Press. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.tallahassee.com/mld/democrat/news/opinion/10323967.htm"&gt;Abstinence-only programs: dishonest and ineffective&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ATallahassee%20Democrat"&gt;Tallahassee Democrat&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, December 3, 2004

</ul>
