Ashish Thomas. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.smh.com.au/news/National/Aborigines-strike-fuel-for-hygiene-deal/2004/12/08/1102182364537.html%3Foneclick%3Dtrue"&gt;Indigenous Australians told to "wash for fuel&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ASydney%20Morning%20Herald"&gt;Sydney Morning Herald&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, 9 December, 2004 
