BULLET::::- David DeBatto. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.salon.com/news/feature/2004/12/08/coverup/print.html"&gt;Whitewashing torture?&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ASalon.com"&gt;Salon.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, December 8,2004

