BULLET::::- Cindy Swirko. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.theledger.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article%3FAID%3D/20041215/NEWS/412150413/1004"&gt;Man Charged With Animal Cruelty After Biting His Dog&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Ledger"&gt;The Ledger&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, December 15, 2004

