BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.msnbc.msn.com/id/6728335/"&gt;Billboard escalates Cuban Christmas crisis&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AMSNBC"&gt;MSNBC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, December 17, 2004

