BULLET::::2. Rone Tempest, &lt;a href="http%3A//pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/646789351.html%3Fdid%3D646789351%26amp%3BFMT%3DABS%26amp%3BFMTS%3DFT%26amp%3Bdate%3DJun%2B5%252C%2B2004%26amp%3Bauthor%3DRone%2BTempest%26amp%3Bdesc%3DTHE%2BCONFLICT%2BIN%2BIRAQ%253B%2BCharges%2Band%2BCountercharges%2Bas%2BSoldier%2BAlleges%2BAbuse%253B%2BA%2BCalifornia%2Bguardsman%2Bsays%2Bhe%2Bwas%2Bhustled%2Bout%2Bof%2BIraq%2Bfor%2Bspeaking%2Bup.%2BThe%2BArmy%2Bsays%2Bhe%2Bhas%2Bmental%2Bproblems.%2BThe%2Bcase%2Bhas%2Bbeen%2Breopened."&gt;Charges and Countercharges as Soldier Alleges Abuse &lt;/a&gt;, Jun 5, 2004, ♡❤Los Angeles Times♡❤.

