BULLET::::2. 30 November, Damián Wroclavsky e Ignacio Badal &lt;a href="http%3A//br.news.yahoo.com/041130/5/pjzl.html"&gt;Chile espera que Argentina expulse guerrilheiro preso&lt;/a&gt;, ♡❤Yahoo News♡❤.
BULLET::::3. 14 February 2002, Marcelo Godoy e Rogério Panda, &lt;a href="http%3A//www.estadao.com.br/agestado/noticias/2002/fev/14/332.htm"&gt;Possível líder do seqüestro de Olivetto fundou a FPRM &lt;/a&gt;, ♡❤AE♡❤.
BULLET::::4. &lt;a href="http%3A//www.tkb.org/Group.jsp%3FgroupID%3D222"&gt;MIPT Terrorism Knowledge Base&lt;/a&gt;
