BULLET::::- ABC News Online. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.abc.net.au/news/newsitems/200412/s1269235.htm"&gt;Bakhtiyaris 'making fools' of Australians&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAustralian%20Broadcasting%20Corporation"&gt;Australian Broadcasting Corporation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, 20 December 2004
BULLET::::- ABC News Online. "&lt;a href="http%3A//abc.net.au/sa/news/200412/s1270681.htm"&gt;Bartlett ends hunger strike&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAustralian%20Broadcasting%20Corporation"&gt;Australian Broadcasting Corporation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, 22 December 2004

</ul>


