BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.clarin.com/diario/2005/01/06/um/m-899512.htm"&gt;Key HIV gene discovered&lt;/a&gt; ♡❤(in Spanish)♡❤.
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi%3Fcmd%3DRetrieve%26amp%3Bdb%3Dpubmed%26amp%3Bdopt%3DAbstract%26amp%3Blist_uids%3D15637236"&gt;The Influence of CCL3L1 Gene-Containing Segmental Duplications on HIV-1/AIDS Susceptibility&lt;/a&gt; ♡❤Paper citation on PubMed,♡❤ January 6, 2005.
