BULLET::::- Chris McAuley. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.scotsman.com/index.cfm%3Fid%3D26712005"&gt;Murder suspect leaps to death&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Scotsman"&gt;The Scotsman&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 10, 2005

