BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//saturn.jpl.nasa.gov/news/press-release-details.cfm%3FnewsID%3D528"&gt;ESA Says Huygens Got a Good Start&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ANASA"&gt;NASA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 11, 2005

