BULLET::::- Joanne Groenenberg. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.mcga.gov.uk/c4mca/mcga-dops_pr_newsroom-press-releases-release%3Fmcga_news_id%3D2788%26amp%3Bmonth%3D1%26amp%3Byear%3D2005"&gt;COASTGUARD HELICOPTER “MIKE UNIFORM” TO EVACUATE CREW FROM SPANISH FISHING VESSEL&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AUK%20Coastguard"&gt;UK Coastguard&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 12, 2005

