BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.laprensahn.com/nacionales.php%3Fid%3D546%26amp%3Btabla%3DJanuary_2005%26amp%3Bfecha%3D20050113"&gt;Ocho mil militares para la seguridad en las elecciones&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3Ala%20Prensahn"&gt;la Prensahn&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, 13 de enero del 2005 www.laprensahn.com (&lt;a href="http%3A//translate.google.com/translate%3Fu%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.laprensahn.com%252Fnacionales.php%253Fid%253D546%2526tabla%253DJanuary_2005%2526fecha%253D20050113%26amp%3Blangpair%3Des%257Cen%26amp%3Bhl%3Den%26amp%3Bie%3DUTF-8%26amp%3Boe%3DUTF-8%26amp%3Bprev%3D%252Flanguage_tools"&gt;Spanish-English translation&lt;/a&gt;)

