</ul>
<ul>
BULLET::::- ♡❤♡♡❤Racing Stripes♡❤ (PG) [1:24]:♡❤♡ Warner Bros. also enters the debut fray with its live-action talking animal family movie, ♡❤&lt;a href="w%3ARacing%20Stripes"&gt;Racing Stripes&lt;/a&gt;♡❤, featuring the voices from such a diverse cast as &lt;a href="w%3ASnoop%20Dogg"&gt;Snoop Dogg&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="w%3AMandy%20Moore"&gt;Mandy Moore&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="w%3ADustin%20Hoffman"&gt;Dustin Hoffman&lt;/a&gt;. ♡❤Racing Stripes♡❤ starts its run with 3,185 venues.

</ul>
<ul>
BULLET::::- ♡❤♡♡❤House of Flying Daggers♡❤ (PG-13) [1:59]:♡❤♡ Sony Pictures Classics is expanding its &lt;a href="w%3AWire%20fu"&gt;wire fu&lt;/a&gt; Chinese war epic, ♡❤&lt;a href="w%3AHouse%20of%20Flying%20Daggers"&gt;House of Flying Daggers&lt;/a&gt;♡❤. The film has made it to several critics best-of-the-year lists and is considered a front runner for Academy Award nominations in several technical categories.

