BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.laprensahn.com/opinion.php%3Fid%3D551%26amp%3Btabla%3DJanuary_2005%26amp%3Bfecha%3D20050114"&gt;Spanish site explaining the situation&lt;/a&gt;

</ul>


