BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.livescience.com/forcesofnature/050114_iceberg_crash.html"&gt;Huge Iceberg to Ram Glacier&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ALiveScience.com"&gt;LiveScience.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 14, 2005
BULLET::::- Bridget Harrison. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.technewsworld.com/story/91336145105984441.html"&gt;Iceberg Crash To Rock Antarctica&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ANew%20York%20Post"&gt;New York Post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 11, 2005

</ul>


