BULLET::::- Janice Tang. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.japantoday.com/e/%3Fcontent%3Dcomment%26amp%3Bid%3D693"&gt;A vicious cycle with China&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AJapan%20Today"&gt;Japan Today&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, December 11, 2004
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.japantimes.co.jp/cgi-bin/getarticle.pl5%3Fnn20040921b1.htm"&gt;More troops to guard southern isles&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Japan%20Times"&gt;The Japan Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, September 21, 2004
BULLET::::- Ho Szu-shen 何思慎. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.taipeitimes.com/News/edit/archives/2004/09/09/2003202223"&gt;China interested in Japan's waters&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ATaipei%20Times"&gt;Taipei Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, September 9, 2004
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.mofa.go.jp/region/asia-paci/senkaku/senkaku.html"&gt;The Basic View on the Sovereignty over the Senkaku Islands&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20of%20Japan"&gt;The Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Japan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, Undated
