BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.gardianul.ro/index.php%3Fa%3Dprimapagina2005011806.xml"&gt;Vecinii se retrag, Băsescu trimite noi trupe în Irak&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AGardianul"&gt;Gardianul&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, January 18, 2005
