<h1>Suspects arrested in Brazilian kidnapping case</h1>
&lt;strong class="published"&gt;&lt;span id="publishDate" class="value-title" title=""&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class="Z3988" style="display:none" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rfr_id=rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikinews.org:User%3ADendodge&amp;rft_id=info:sid/en.wikinews.org:&amp;rft.atitle=Suspects%20arrested%20in%20Brazilian%20kidnapping%20case&amp;rft.jtitle=Wikinews&amp;rft.date=&amp;rft.aucorp=Wikinews+contributors&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.rights=CC-BY+2.5&amp;rft.identifier=&amp;rft.artnum="&gt; &lt;/span&gt; 

São Paulo, &lt;a href="Brazil"&gt;Brazil&lt;/a&gt; – Thursday night (January, 13), &lt;a href="w%3AS%C3%A3o%20Paulo"&gt;São Paulo&lt;/a&gt; police officers arrested four men in a supermarket in &lt;a href="w%3AS%C3%A3o%20Caetano%20do%20Sul"&gt;São Caetano do Sul&lt;/a&gt;. According to the police the men are suspect of kidnapping &lt;a href="w%3AMarina%20da%20Silva%20Souza"&gt;Marina da Silva Souza&lt;/a&gt;, aged 44, mother of the celebrity Brazilian &lt;a href="w%3Asoccer"&gt;soccer&lt;/a&gt; player of &lt;a href="w%3ASantos%20Futebol%20Clube"&gt;Santos Football Club&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="w%3ARobinho"&gt;Robinho&lt;/a&gt;.

