BULLET::::- CTV.ca News Staff. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.ctv.ca/servlet/ArticleNews/story/CTVNews/1106095730331_7/%3Fhub%3DTopStories"&gt;Torrential downpours causing havoc in B.C.&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACTV.ca"&gt;CTV.ca&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, Tue. Jan. 18 2005 11:21 PM ET
